<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-86-1125 </DOCNO><TEXT>The problems of using gastroroentgenology for improvement of the diagnosisof gastric tumors and ulcers are considered. Advantages of gastrofluorographyin the mentioned diagnosis are evaluated. It is shown, that nowadaysgastrofluorography should become an obligatory element of diagnosis measurementsaimed at increase of efficiency of gastric tumor and ulcer disclosure.</TEXT></DOC>